 Dependencies: NONE — Python standard library only (csv, json, ssl, urllib)
               Tested on Python 3.6+ / RHEL air-gapped environment.

 Output files (written to ./gitlab_audit_<timestamp>/ folder):
   01_dashboard.csv          — Summary counts per metric
   02_full_audit.csv         — Every repo x every artifact count
   03_migration_plan.csv     — Checklist sorted HIGH > MEDIUM > LOW > ARCHIVED
   04_cicd_repos.csv         — Only repos with CI/CD pipelines
   05_open_items.csv         — Repos with open MRs or open Issues
   06_branches_tags.csv      — Branch and tag counts per repo
   07_access_config.csv      — Members, webhooks, deploy keys, protected branches
   audit_report.html         — Single-file HTML report (open in browser, no internet)

 Usage:
   1. Set TOKEN and TARGET_GROUP below.
   2. python3 fetch_repos_audit.py
=============================================================================
"""

